}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== This is the original DSS-8+ revision. It has a nice brown-ish metal case (.. though it seems some later revisions of the DSS-8+ also use the same case). :It has 8 Switch ports and one uplink port.
"DSS-8" and "REV-B1" is silkscreened on the top of one particular unit's board. :"8DSS8....1B1", "MADE IN TAIWAN", and a date code of '''9929''' is etched onto the bottom. :The fan used on this unit is a '''SUNON''' KD0502PFB3-8.
The main Switch IC is covered by a large heatsink. <!-- which I have not removed -->
